  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbf!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An old man died after being caught in an electric fence for an elephant.",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Vaunadivu Povisar has reported that an old man died early today (24) after being attacked by a misara in Bhavakkodisenai area of \u200b\u200bVaunadivu Police Division of Batticaloa District.",
        "Ganapathipillai Chinnathambi, a father of two children (71) from Kokkaticholai area of \u200b\u200bMudailakuda, died in the accident.",
        "It has been revealed during the initial investigations of the police that the said person was taking care of a friend's garden compound, cows and goats and was found dead by a fish fence placed for elephants to protect the garden.",
        "According to the order of Batticaloa District Court Judge Peter Boll, Mandur Division Sudden Death Investigation Officer Thampipillai Tavakumar visited the body and ordered the police to hand over the body to the relatives after post-mortem examination."
      ],
